; This query assumes that higher total access counts and average temperatures indicate greater importance or relevance of the weather data; 
; The "latest version number" and "version count" are considered important for understanding the data's reliability and update history;
; "Data collection frequency" is crucial for determining how often weather data is updated at each station.

sql:
SELECT station_name
FROM weather_stations
ORDER BY station_name ASC;
